To invite a person to be your contact:
1 - Make sure the Contacts tab is selected.
2 - Click the 'Contacts' link on the Contacts tab.
3 - In the dialog that appears, type the e-mail of the person you wish to invite.
4 - Click the 'Invite' button. The person will receive an invitation.

<p>There are two other ways you can invite a person to be your contact.
  * Type the person's e-mail address in the publish dialog, when you are publishing a package.
  * Expand a package, right click on the person you would like to invite, and select 'invite' from the menu.